com.crawljax.util

Class DomHistoryElement

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.crawljax.util.DomHistoryElement

  • public class DomHistoryElement
extends Object
    DomHistoryElement contain a string representation of the DOM and the Document representation. The active element is not explicitly stored because it can always be found by searching for the element which has the requestForProxyId attribute.
